title: Who will Sam Frost choose in The Bachelorette grand final?
text:
Who will Sam Frost choose in The Bachelorette grand final? Seanna Cronin | 22nd Oct 2015 6:00 AM Seanna Cronin APN Entertainment Editor A US ex-pat, Seanna has been writing about the Australian entertainment industries for the past six years and is also a documentary producer, photographer and scuba diver. Sam Frost stars in the TV series The Bachelorette. Channel 10 Local Real Estate Subscribe Now 
SAM Frost is head over heels for her new beau and tonight viewers will finally see which man has stolen her heart. 
Tonight's grand final of the hit reality dating show will see the 26-year-old choose between her final two suitors: construction manager Sasha Mielczarek and real estate agent and soccer player Michael Turnbull. 
Last night's episode saw Frost farewell Perth rope technician Richie Strahan, a favourite amongst many viewers for his sense of humour. 
It looks to be a close race with fans tipping Mielczarek by a small margin on the show's love leaderboard. Reader poll Who will win The Bachelorette? Sasha
